Comment: 1,0:00:01.62,0:00:04.71,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,现在开始 不同的未来
Comment: 1,0:00:04.82,0:00:07.31,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,手握缥缈的希望
Comment: 1,0:00:07.50,0:00:10.44,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,朝崖边前进吧
Comment: 1,0:00:10.68,0:00:16.24,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,山崖的对面是鲜花盛开
Comment: 1,0:00:24.72,0:00:27.72,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,心里罗列着
Comment: 1,0:00:27.72,0:00:30.26,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,渺小却又伟大的梦想
Comment: 1,0:00:30.66,0:00:33.47,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,在不时迷茫与跌倒中
Comment: 1,0:00:33.81,0:00:36.16,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,踏出了属于自己的路
Comment: 1,0:00:36.59,0:00:39.52,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,所谓的脆弱
Comment: 1,0:00:39.52,0:00:42.26,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,并非是失败
Comment: 1,0:00:42.55,0:00:45.26,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,而是放弃
Comment: 1,0:00:45.56,0:00:49.36,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,在与自我的一对一决斗中
Comment: 1,0:00:49.74,0:00:53.41,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,仅有的胜算
Comment: 1,0:00:53.41,0:00:55.05,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,仍然存在于
Comment: 1,0:00:55.30,0:01:00.14,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,这双手上
Comment: 1,0:01:00.88,0:01:03.74,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,现在开始 大胆逆转
Comment: 1,0:01:03.98,0:01:06.67,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,胜利并非是奇迹
Comment: 1,0:01:06.77,0:01:09.66,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,只因竭尽全力
Comment: 1,0:01:09.94,0:01:12.54,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,不断挑战
Comment: 1,0:01:12.75,0:01:15.57,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,现在开始 胜负未定
Comment: 1,0:01:15.85,0:01:18.37,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要渴望荣光
Comment: 1,0:01:18.60,0:01:21.50,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,朝崖边前进吧
Comment: 1,0:01:21.72,0:01:25.38,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,山崖的对面是鲜花盛开
Comment: 1,0:01:25.70,0:01:27.76,ZH,,0,0,0,karaoke,一定
